<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>LUNGLAWMHNAK IN KAN IN THANGTHAT CH37</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lunglawmhnak in kan in thangthat, Sunpar Pathian dawtnak Bawi, Pangpar
 ni hoih in a par bang, Kan lung panh in umter ko, Sual le ngaihchiat
 minmei tianter, Zumh khawh lonak muihnak zong, a hmunmi lung lawmhnak
 petu, Ni ceunak run kan pe tuah.

[V2]
 Na sermi nih an in thangthat, Lei le van na cerh dih hna, Arfi le
 vanmi hla an sa, Thangthat dai lo Bawi na si, Lo le tupi, nel le
 fingtlang, Ramlak pangpar rili luang, va hramthiam le cerhti luang nih,
 Nangmah lawmh awk an kan sawm.

[V3]
 Leicung mi lawmhnak hla sa u, Deirel arfi an sakmi, Kan Pa dawtnak nih
 a kan pen, Unau dawtnih a kan tem, Hlasak in hmaiah kan fong chin, Harnak
 ah teitu kan si, ni lei ah hla nih a kan hruai, Teinak nunnak hla a si.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<hymn_number>37</hymn_number>
</song>